Title: When the Cramer-Rao Inequality provides no information
Authors: Steven J. Miller
Categories: math.ST stat.TH
Comments: 10 pages, 1 figure, to appear in Communications in Information and
  Systems
Journal-ref: Communications in Information and Systems 7 (2007), no. 3,
  265--272
\\
  We investigate a one-parameter family of probability densities (related to
the Pareto distribution, which describes many natural phenomena) where the
Cramer-Rao inequality provides no information.
